message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. Given its exceptional value and quality, it's worth more than $12,000 to you, but we're looking to make this transaction beneficial for both parties. Considering the market value and the unique benefits this product offers, I would like to propose a price of $10,000 for it. This price reflects the product's worth while also allowing us to achieve a fair profit. Please let me know if this offer meets your expectations or if there's anything else I can assist you with.
